sentence: 不过，张小碗馄饨，苏天河也不矫情，接过食盒看了一眼，沈青鸾没说什么，略带羞涩地笑了一下，你呀，有心了。 But, Zhang's wonton, Su Tianhe didn't beat around the bush, took the food box and took a look, Shen Qingluan didn't say anything, smiled a little shyly, you are so considerate. 苏天河恍然，似有深意地指了一下沈青鸾，这两家餐馆可距离不近，而且看包装不像是外卖，食盒也是另外准备的。 Su Tianhe suddenly realized, pointed at Shen Qingluan with profound meaning, these two restaurants are not close, and judging from the packaging, it doesn't look like takeout, the food box was also prepared separately. 苏总不介意就好。 It's good that Mr. Su doesn't mind. 那我先回工位了。 Then I'll go back to my workstation first. 沈青鸾俏皮的眨眨眼，转身欲走。 Shen Qingluan blinked playfully, turned to leave. 不着急回去，你提任人事主管的事情有消息了，跟我来。 No rush to go back, there's news about your promotion to HR supervisor, follow me. 啊，真的啊？ Really?
source: This appears to be a dialogue excerpt from a Chinese corporate romance or drama series, possibly an office setting scene.

sentence: Shen Qingluan was ecstatic, and out of excitement, she grabbed Su Changhe's arm. 啊，抱歉，我失态了。 Sorry, I lost my composure. 哈哈，年轻人，不过我提醒你，目前也只是任命你暂代人事主管的位置，具体的任职文件还要等新老板来了才行。 Young man, let me remind you, you are only temporarily appointed as the head of HR, and the specific appointment document will have to wait for the new boss to arrive. 苏长河深深地吸了口气，看似无意地拍了拍沈青鸾的肩膀。 Su Changhe took a deep breath and patted Shen Qingluan's shoulder seemingly casually. 我知道的，我一定不会让苏总失望的。 I know, I won't let Mr. Su down. 不过新老板还没来吗？ Hasn't the new boss arrived yet?
